title: Latest news & Divisional Playoff concerns
itunes:title: Latest news & Divisional Playoff concerns
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- breakdown the Divisional Playoff Round and share their concerns about Cam Newton's mechanics and how DeMarco Murray will handle the Packers defense. Plus, they rank the remaining eight quarterbacks who are still in the playoffs.
